config BR2_PACKAGE_NDSEND
	bool "ndsend package"
	default n
	help
	  ndsend - send a Neighbor Advertisement NDP packet 
          The ndsend utility is called by arpsend(8) for IPv6 addresses to send an unsolicited Neighbor
          Advertisement ICMPv6 multicast packet announcing a given IPv6 address to all  IPv6  nodes  as
          per RFC4861.
          Source Code: http://download.openvz.org/utils/vzctl/current/src/
